title: The 90's Bracket (Part One)
description: Inspired by The Last Dance and Pogs, the KAJ head back to the bracket. First, they discuss their worst sports memories (4:53), then dive into a 32-seed bracket of the best things from the 90's (22:32). Later, a voicemail about Kristin Cavallari and Jay Cutler (1:46:20).
